= Tor Controller =

Two options. '''Arm''' or Vidalia. '''Arm''' is already '''pre-installed''' on Whonix and '''recommended'''.

= Vidalia =

'''Not recommend.''' Better use Arm. See below.

<font size="-3">See [[#vidalia|Vidalia]].</font>

= Arm =

Since Whonix does not include Vidalia, Arm is '''recommended'''. It's already pre-installed on Whonix-Gateway.

[[Image:screenshot_arm_page1_cropped.png|arm, Tor Controller|thumb]]

To start it, simply type on Whonix-Gateway:

<pre>sudo arm</pre>

To get a new circuit, press.

<pre>n</pre>

